<div class="tag">
<a href="https://www.gushiwen.org/shiwen/default.aspx?tstr=%e8%af%97%e7%bb%8f">诗经</a>
<span>，</span><a href="https://www.gushiwen.org/shiwen/default.aspx?tstr=%e5%86%99%e8%8a%b1">写花</a>
<span>，</span><a href="https://www.gushiwen.org/shiwen/default.aspx?tstr=%e8%b5%9e%e7%be%8e">赞美</a>
<span>，</span><a href="https://www.gushiwen.org/shiwen/default.aspx?tstr=%e5%86%99%e4%ba%ba">写人</a>
</div>
